description:
&lt;p&gt;The development of a new service at Park House, North Manchester General Hospital has led to a post becoming available for a Band 6 Physical Healthcare Lead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The new Physical Healthcare Team will consist of one Band 6 and four band 4 Assistant Practitioners, who will provide physical health support, investigations and education to seven mental health acute inpatient services located within Park House.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post-holder will ideally be either by a qualified RGN, dual trained RN or RMN with a background within physical health care. The post holder will ensure that all physical health care CQUINS and KPI’s are met. They will provide specialist expertise within part of the MDT for the care-planning of those with complex physical health needs and arrange training where required for inpatient staff members. This should include but is not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Equipment knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Infection Control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tissue Viability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nutritional MUST screening tool&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PHIT tool&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diabetes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical Assessment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;COPD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ANTT&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The postholder will be responsible for the line management and supervision of the band 4 practitioners. The postholder will also be expected to contribute towards the design and development of standard operating procedures to guide physical health care and the physical health team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be required to work, for the majority of time, as an autonomous clinical practitioner for patient groups across a range of clinical settings. The post holder will be expected to forge strong links with the Central Nursing and AHP Team and physical health care providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hope that you will be able to join us at this exciting time to lead and assist to establish this new service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Hazel Preston&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Inpatient Operational Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: hazel.preston@gmmh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 0161 271 0273&lt;/p&gt;
